/ul><h4>4.4.1 – December 5, 2016</h4><ul><li>Added: <code>network_get_term()</code> function, the <code>get_term()</code> equivalent. The first parameter is $blog_id.</li></ul><h4>4.4 – December 4, 2016</h4><ul><li>Now you can completely replace the website default search results with the global network search results in the plugin settings without code at all.</li><li>As an option you can use both default and global search widgets in your website sidebar.</li></ul><h4>4.3.1 – November 15, 2016</h4><ul><li>Fixed: Warnings when indexing post meta.</li></ul><h4>4.3 – November 7, 2016</h4><ul><li>Improved: Plugin option pages are optimized for both new and old versions of WordPress.</li><li>Improved: Plugin performance in /wp-admin/.</li><li>Fixed: Problem with database tables, when default WordPress database has uncommon columns.</li><li>Fixed: Problem when saving blog index settings caused by WP-Cirrus plugin.</li></ul><h4>4.2 – September 23, 2016</h4><ul><li>Bug fixes.</li><li>Plugin update improvements.</li></ul><h4>4.1.2</h4><ul><li>Now the <code>blog_id</code> parameter of <code>Network_Query</code> supports array values.</li></ul><h4>4.1.1</h4><ul><li>Fixed redirect location for manual updates check.</li></ul><h4>4.1</h4><ul><li>Code optimization and UI improvements.</li></ul><h4>4.0</h4><ul><li>You can now get terms (categories, post_tags etc) from all blogs in Multisite network in a one loop using network_get_terms() function.</li><li>Changes in plugin update mechanism.</li></ul><h4>3.1</h4><ul><li>Changes in plugin update mechanism.</li></ul>\",\n		\"screenshots\" : \"<ol><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/custom-post-types-to-index-for-each-blog.gif?rev=1536934801\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/custom-post-types-to-index-for-each-blog.gif?rev=1536934801\' alt=\'For each blog you can choose what post types to index or completely disable indexing.\' /></a><p>For each blog you can choose what post types to index or completely disable indexing.</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/column-blog-id.png?rev=1524129593\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/column-blog-id.png?rev=1524129593\' alt=\'Plugin automatically adds the Blog ID column to the table with the all websites.\' /></a><p>Plugin automatically adds the Blog ID column to the table with the all websites.</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/global-settings-multisite-search.png?rev=1524129072\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/global-settings-multisite-search.png?rev=1524129072\' alt=\'If you use the Widget option, the Global Search Widget will appear in Appearance &gt; Widgets, or if you would like to replace the default search results with the global ones, you should proceed to the Sites admin page and turn this feature on there for each site individually.\' /></a><p>If you use the Widget option, the Global Search Widget will appear in Appearance &gt; Widgets, or if you would like to replace the default search results with the global ones, you should proceed to the Sites admin page and turn this feature on there for each site individually.</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/multisite-dashboard.png?rev=1524128751\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/multisite-dashboard.png?rev=1524128751\' alt=\'Network Index Statistics in Dashboard.\' /></a><p>Network Index Statistics in Dashboard.</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rebuild-index.png?rev=1524128335\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rebuild-index.png?rev=1524128335\' alt=\'That’s where you can completely rebuild the index.\' /></a><p>That’s where you can completely rebuild the index.</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/network-posts-database.png?rev=1524128098\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/network-posts-database.png?rev=1524128098\' alt=\'MySQL database with the global content inside phpMyAdmin\' /></a><p>MySQL database with the global content inside phpMyAdmin</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/specific-website-customization.png?rev=1480873747\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/specific-website-customization.png?rev=1480873747\' alt=\'specific-website-customization\' /></a><p>specific-website-customization</p></li><li><a href=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/posts-from-all-blogs.png?rev=1459671817\' target=\'_blank\'><img src=\'https://rudrastyh.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/posts-from-all-blogs.png?rev=1459671817\' alt=\'posts-from-all-blogs\' /></a><p>posts-from-all-blogs</p></li></ol>\"\n	}\n}\";s:7:\"headers\";O:25:\"Requests_Response_Headers\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:7:{s:4:\"vary\";a:1:{i:0;s:23:\"Accept-Encoding, Cookie\";}s:12:\"content-type\";a:1:{i:0;s:16:\"application/json\";}s:14:\"content-length\";a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"7852\";}s:4:\"date\";a:1:{i:0;s:29:\"Tue, 18 Jun 2019 22:13:52 GMT\";}s:6:\"server\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LiteSpeed\";}s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";a:1:{i:0;s:44:\"max-age=10886400; includeSubDomains; preload\";}s:7:\"alt-svc\";a:1:{i:0;s:40:\"quic=\":443\"; ma=2592000; v=\"35,39,43,44\"\";}}}s:11:\"status_code\";i:200;s:16:\"protocol_version\";d:1.100000000000000088817841970012523233890533447265625;s:7:\"success\";b:1;s:9:\"redirects\";i:0;s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"https://rudrastyh.com/infojson.php?plg=1272&e=web%40ereerea.om\";s:7:\"history\";a:0:{}s:7:\"cookies\";O:19:\"Requests_Cookie_Jar\":1:{s:10:\"\0*\0cookies\";a:0:{}}}s:11:\"\0*\0filename\";N;s:4:\"data\";N;s:7:\"headers\";N;s:6:\"status\";N;}}', 'no'),
